OL,3,C'Grave concerns' about council's
OL,4,Chandling of special educational needs
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FBy: Helen Keenan, ITV News London
OL,8,Freporter
OL,10,FThe Government is being urged to
OL,11,Fintervene after 'grave concerns' were
OL,12,Fraised over Surrey County Council's
OL,13,Fhandling of special educational needs
OL,14,Fprovisions.
OL,16,FSix Liberal Democrat Surrey MPs have
OL,17,Fjointly written to the Education
OL,18,FSecretary asking her to protect Surrey
OL,19,Fchildren from harm and accused the
OL,20,Fcounty council of treating families
OL,21,Fwith contempt.
