OL,3,C'Grave concerns' about council's
OL,4,Chandling of special educational needs
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FAccording to the letter, Surrey County
OL,8,FCouncil has the highest number of
OL,9,Fcomplaints in the country about its
OL,10,FSEND provision to the Local Government
OL,11,FOmbudsman.
OL,13,FThe MPs are accusing the council of
OL,14,Faltering the number of complaints
OL,15,Fabout their SEND provision to make
OL,16,Fthem look smaller. The allegation is
OL,17,Fsupported by parents.
