OL,7,FNatalie has autism and ADHD and has
OL,8,Ftried to take her own life twelve
OL,9,Ftimes and her mother claims she was
OL,10,Frefused the medication she needs that
OL,11,Fmay have helped her stay in a
OL,12,Fmainstream school.
OL,14,FShe says her support provision was
OL,15,Fpulled unexpectedly and she doesn't
OL,16,Fhave access to an education package
OL,17,Ffrom Surrey County Council.
