OL,7,FJen Bridges-Chalkley had autism and
OL,8,FADHD, she died by suicide in October
OL,9,F2021, and her mother says Jen took her
OL,10,Fown life because her mental health had
OL,11,Fsuffered so badly.
OL,13,FSharren Bridges says SEND provision in
OL,14,FSurrey has only got worse since her
OL,15,Fdaughter's death.
OL,17,FAccording to Surrey's coroner the 17-
OL,18,Fyear-old's death could have been
OL,19,Favoided if support had been provided
OL,20,Fin a "timely manner".
