OL,7,FThe coroner said he was satisfied
OL,8,Fthat, had specialist input been
OL,9,Fprovided , the teenager's final crisis
OL,10,Fwould "probably have been avoided or
OL,11,Fmanaged, such as to avoid her death".
OL,13,FSharren has chosen to speak out
OL,14,Fbecause she is concerned other
OL,15,Fchildren could face the same outcome
OL,16,Fas her daughter and said: "If people
OL,17,Fhad done their job there is every
OL,18,Fchance Jen could still be alive. I
OL,19,Fwould have a 21 year old daughter now,
OL,20,Fnot a daughter who is forever 17."
