OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FSurrey County Council have responded
OL,8,Fto the accusations of altering their
OL,9,Fcomplaints figures saying: "We
OL,10,Fstrongly refute this accusation.
OL,12,F"Surrey County Council is fully
OL,13,Ftransparent in its reporting around
OL,14,Fcomplaints data, in particular in
OL,15,Fbenchmarking, which goes further than
OL,16,Fmany other local authorities. This is
OL,17,Fpublicly available data and is
OL,18,Fincluded in the report from September
OL,19,F2024."
