OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FThe council gave this statement
OL,8,Fregarding SEND provision in the
OL,9,FCounty: "Provision and support for
OL,10,Fchildren with AND is a systemic issue
OL,11,Fthat councils up and down the country
OL,12,Fare grappling with. The national
OL,13,Fsystem is not working for families,
OL,14,Fschools or councils, and we and other
OL,15,Fbodies are consistently lobbying
OL,16,Fgovernment for wider system changes,
OL,17,Fadditional funding and urgent reform.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
