OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,F"Alongside this, we are working
OL,8,Fextremely hard here in Surrey to
OL,9,Fimprove our services for children with
OL,10,Fadditional needs and disabilities. In
OL,11,FSeptember 2023 we invested an
OL,12,Fadditional #15m into a three-year
OL,13,Fmulti-agency recovery plan, which is
OL,14,Fnow showing clear performance
OL,15,Fimprovements. We are recruiting more
OL,16,Fprofessionals in shortage areas,
OL,17,Fbuilding new specialist school places
OL,18,Fand reviewing every aspect of the SEND
OL,19,Fsystem within our control.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
