OL,7,FAfter receiving the letter the
OL,8,FDepartment for Education told ITV News
OL,9,FLondon that keeping children safe
OL,10,Fshould be the utmost priority for all
OL,11,Flocal authorities, adding: "We are
OL,12,Fworking closely to support and
OL,13,Fchallenge Surrey County Council to
OL,14,Fimprove the delivery of its SEND and
OL,15,Fchild protection services."
